{"tid":2134227,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"退休檢控官被指踢凹的士罪成罰款　上訴得直撤罪","createTime":"2020-07-31T14:16:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-31T14:28:01.000Z","uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"d86592e3c4b7d674ab8284390e84c5db28086544","tid":2134227,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:16:55.000Z","msg":"律政司退休高級檢控官布偉倫（Edward Joshua Brook）前年3月在蘭桂坊疑因遭司機拒載而起爭執，涉踢凹的士左邊車身，去年被裁定一項刑事損壞罪成，罰款3000元以及賠償4500元維修費。布偉倫早前向高等法院就定罪提出上訴，上訴庭今（31日）頒下判辭，裁定布偉倫上訴得直，撤銷定罪和判刑。<br />\n<br />\n上訴人布偉倫原被控於2018年3月16日，在中環雲咸街55號無合法辯解而損毁一部的士，翌年在裁判法院經審訊後被判罪成。<br />\n<br />\n高院法官金貝理在判辭指出，審視證人口供及法庭聆訊謄本後，發現涉案的士司機的供辭有太多不一致及難以信納的地方，認為未能維持原有控罪。金官續稱，被告雖承認踢到的士車身，但至於車身損壞是否由被告行為所造成，在原審時並沒有處理清楚，認為定罪未能達至毫無合理懷疑，裁定布偉倫上訴得直。<br />\n<br />\nsource: 明報"},{"pid":"6d81417ff86bc5a6cb991c121657a7ed53c4e029","tid":2134227,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"特權階層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86d4c6ec533bcf34e3814174f841c0b233ffaeb3","tid":2134227,"uid":240362,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6d81417ff86bc5a6cb991c121657a7ed53c4e029","tid":2134227,"uid":21545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"特權階層<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-31T14:18:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a138713d2a22da34289e40394172e286eaa751","tid":2134227,"uid":30720